   <head>To the Christian Reader.</head>
   <p>TO auoyd all doubt of de<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ceit (Christian Reader) which might bee thought to lie lurking vnder this glorious title, <hi>The Conduit of Com<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>fort,</hi> we will make an Ana<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>tomie of this Encheridion, or Manuel, opening the very body, &amp; laying out the bowels thereof before the eyes of thy iudgement. Note therefore euery member, for thy full sa<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>tisfaction, as followeth.</p>
